{"tid":198763,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[做足準備]祖記提前為次回合作客巴塞，提交12碼與紅牌上訴文件","createTime":"2017-04-12T17:26:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-19T13:39:58.000Z","uid":28938,"like":50,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cc2d79d005f6052adede64e26355047f50070e16","tid":198763,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T17:26:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H3H31w2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH3H31w2.jpg&h=ce1123f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>祖記提前為次回合作客巴塞，提交12碼與紅牌上訴文件</strong><br />\n<br />\n[01:10] 首回合主場3:0大勝巴塞隆拿，祖雲達斯領隊艾歷利表示滿意斑馬軍團的整體表現，特別是後防球員成功實踐了高壓戰術，限制了MSN發揮。<br />\n<br />\n展望次回合，該名領隊續道：「第二回合作客球賽將非常艱難，魯營的主場威力是毋庸置疑的。為此我們已預先向歐洲足球協會(UEFA)提交上訴文件，預備可能會面對被判12碼或紅牌的情況。」<br />\n<br />\n艾歷利補充：「我絕對不是指球證會偏幫巴塞隆拿，但看了早前巴黎聖日耳門被逆轉的那場比賽後，你就知道在魯營，什麼都可能會發生。」"},{"pid":"1509d40c623f57f3767953f9813e227a681cd529","tid":198763,"uid":70441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T17:31:17.000Z","msg":"祖雲入得個3球算唔算輸左9成 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a845eccf613575371a10e7d71e29c192fa714ff0","tid":198763,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T17:33:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>祖雲入得個3球算唔算輸左9成 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n估唔到艾歷利講得咁白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09a0bd00a46e14dec31b25b1a977b81540fe1607","tid":198763,"uid":82698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T17:41:56.000Z","msg":"其實祖記今季自己咪又係食左好多球12碼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n黑鬥黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ed6acbf3d1092ce61bb41431c452f0bf4c1d807","tid":198763,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T17:51:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實祖記今季自己咪又係食左好多